sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant View as View Index/Form
    participant Controller as KeuanganController
    participant Model as Keuangan Model
    participant Storage as File Storage
    participant DB as Database
    
    Admin->>View: Buka Menu Keuangan
    View->>Controller: GET /admin/keuangan
    Controller->>Model: Query (Filter Role/Search)
    Model-->>Controller: Return Data
    Controller-->>View: Render List
    
    opt Tambah Transaksi
        Admin->>View: Klik Tambah
        View->>Controller: GET /create
        Controller-->>View: Form Create
        
        Admin->>View: Submit Data (incl. File)
        View->>Controller: POST /store
        
        Note right of Controller: Normalisasi Mata Uang (Remove dots/commas)
        
        opt Ada File Bukti
            Controller->>Storage: Put File
            Storage-->>Controller: Path File
        end
        
        Controller->>Model: Create(Data)
        Model->>DB: Insert
        DB-->>Model: Success
        Controller-->>View: Redirect with Success
    end
    
    opt Lihat Laporan
        Admin->>View: Buka Menu Laporan
        View->>Controller: GET /report
        Controller->>Model: Calculate Sum & Group By Date
        Model-->>Controller: Aggregated Data
        Controller-->>View: Render Charts (Chart.js Data)
    end
